keyFacts: The document is a hardware label/serial record for a 2.0TB Western Digital Gold SATA hard drive (model WD2005FBYZ).
The drive has a World Wide Name (WWN): 5001dEE0AEF7941A and a date stamp of December 30, 2016.
The drive is noted as a 'Product of Malaysia' and lists a location in Noorddorp, Netherlands.
The document contains technical specifications including voltage, cache size, and patent numbers.
The file is part of the Epstein case document set (EFTA00002537) but contains no narrative text about persons or events related to the case.
